{{#extend "project" }}
{{#content "title" mode="append"}} - Unscan{{/content}}
{{#content "body-class" mode="append"}} page-unscan{{/content}}
{{#content "backgrounds" mode="append"}}
<li class="background-unscan-hero"></li>
<li class="background-unscan-brand"></li>
<li class="background-unscan-imagery"></li>
<li class="background-unscan-web"></li>
{{/content}}
{{#content "sections" mode="prepend"}}
<li class="animated-section project-hero section-unscan-hero" data-section-id="unscan-hero">
    <div class="content">
        <h1 class="project-title sc-text">Unscan</h1>
        <div class="project-img-wrapper">
            <img src="/img/unscan/unscan-macbook.png" alt="Unscan">
            <ul class="services">
                <li class="sc-text">Brand Identity</li>
                <li class="sc-text">UI/UX Design</li>
                <li class="sc-text">Web Development</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="project-summary sc-text">Minimill developed a confident identity through logo and web for Unscan to reflect their forward-thinking mission of automating large-scale human document processing.</p>
        <blockquote class="sbd-accent">
            <div class="quote-upper-line sbg-accent"></div>
            <div class="quote-mark sf-svg-accent">{{> "icons/quote.svg"}}</div>
            <div class="quote-lower-line sbg-accent"></div>

            <span class="sc-text">Minimill's branding work with Unscan has meant more inbound sales interest and increased trust in our service. We're very happy with their work, and would gladly be a repeat customer.</span>
            <cite>
                <span class="name sc-text">Shariq Hashme</span>
                <span class="title sc-text">Co-Founder, Unscan</span>
                <span class="photo"><img src="/img/unscan/head-shariq.png" alt="Shariq Hashme"></span>
            </cite>
        </blockquote>
    </div>
</li>
<li class="animated-section project-section section-unscan-brand" data-section-id="unscan-brand">
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="h1 sc-text">Locking security into the brand</h2>
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <p class="large sc-text">As an emerging startup, we wanted Unscan’s identity to instill customer trust, vitally important in the finance industry. Their document automation services are hinted through the “U” glyph, while the sharp and formal logotype reinforces that the company is serious about precision and security.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <img class="project-screenshot padded" src="/img/unscan/unscan-logotype.svg" alt="Unscan Logotype">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-12">
            {{#embed "external-link"
                iconClass="quote"}}
                {{#content "icon"}}{{> "icons/quote.svg" }}{{/content}}
                {{#content "h2"}}It was sometimes hard for us to imagine how a manufactured brand could convey values like security and reliability until we worked with the fine folks of Minimill.{{/content}}
                {{#content "cite"}}
                  <span class="photo"><img src="/img/unscan/head-richard.png" alt="Richard Higgins"></span>
                  <span class="name sc-text">Richard Higgins</span>
                  <span class="title sc-text">Co-Founder, Unscan</span>
                {{/content}}
            {{/embed}}
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content color-blocks">
        <div class="col-12">
            {{> color-block
              name="Gold"
              hex="F2BE55"
              class="light"}}
            {{> color-block
              name="Blue"
              hex="6998C3"
              class="dark"}}
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
            {{> color-block
              name="Black"
              hex="222222"
              class="dark with-border"}}
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
            {{> color-block
              name="White"
              hex="FFFFFF"
              class="light"}}
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content font-stacks">
      <div class="col-12">
        {{> font-stack
          name="Standard CT"
          weight="Regular"
          src="/img/unscan/text-unscan-standard.png" }}
        {{> font-stack
          name="Standard CT"
          weight="Bold"
          src="/img/unscan/text-unscan-standardbold.png" }}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</li>
<li class="animated-section project-section section-unscan-imagery" data-section-id="unscan-imagery">
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="h1 sc-text">Illustrating service and values through imagery</h2>
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <p class="large sc-text">In order to display the full features of Unscan, we outlined product components with custom illustrations and iconography. User education is made simple through visual walkthroughs and a unique image style that breaks down highly technical concepts and reaches back to the brand identity.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
          <img class="project-screenshot" src="/img/unscan/unscan-illustrations-animation.gif" alt="Unscan Illustrations">
        </div>
        <div class="col-12">
            <img class="project-screenshot" src="/img/unscan/testimonial-photo.png" alt="Unscan Testimonial Photo">
            <img class="project-screenshot" src="/img/unscan/office-photo.png" alt="Unscan Office Photo">
        </div>
    </div>
</li>
<li class="animated-section project-section section-unscan-web" data-section-id="unscan-web">
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="h1 sc-text">Designing for content flow</h2>
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <p class="large sc-text">With customers in finance and security, the website we created is as much about content as it is about building confidence. The design focuses on the story created by the content, backed by a regal colorway and luxurious gradient style. The site moves users from introductory information to the onboarding call-to-action.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-12">
            <img class="project-screenshot" src="/img/unscan/unscan-monitor.png" alt="Fin">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            {{#embed "external-link"
                href="https://unscan.com/"
                iconClass="link"}}
                {{#content "icon"}}{{> "icons/link.svg" }}{{/content}}
                {{#content "h2"}}unscan.com{{/content}}
            {{/embed}}
        </div>
    </div>
</li>
{{> "footer" class="solid" id="unscan-footer" }}
{{/content}}
{{/extend}}
